All original code is located in the "src" subdirectory, copyright 2015 Thomas Smith.

All code adapted from 3rd-party libraries is located in the "deps" subdirectory.
The adaptations were made by Thomas Smith, with the original authors credited below.

All dependencies included in the source tree have licenses compatible with the GPL V3.

Waf build system:
https://waf.io/
Authors: Thomas Nagy et al.
License: New BSD

Directory: deps/aubio
The aubio library can be found at:
http://aubio.org/
Author: Paul Brossier
License: GPL V3

Directory: deps/coreaudio
This directory contains code that calls Apple's CoreAudio library, based on documentation found at:
http://kaniini.dereferenced.org/2014/08/31/CoreAudio-sucks.html

Directory: deps/jack
The libjack library can be found at:
https://github.com/jackaudio
Authors: Paul Davis et al.
License: LGPL
The dlang-jack wrapper is adapted from:
https://github.com/martinez/dlang-jack
Author: Denis Martinez
License: BSL-1.0

Directory: deps/meters
The metering code is adapted from:
https://github.com/x42/meters.lv2
Author: Robin Gareus
License: GPL V2

Directory: deps/portaudio
The portaudio library can be found at:
http://portaudio.com/
Authors: Ross Bencina, Phil Burk
License: MIT
The portaudio wrapper is adapted from:
https://github.com/D-Programming-Deimos/portaudio
Authors: Walter Bright, Martin Nowak
License: MIT

Directory: deps/rubberband
The rubberband library can be found at:
http://breakfastquay.com/rubberband/
Author: Chris Cannam
License: GPL V2

Directory: deps/samplerate
The samplerate library can be found at:
http://www.mega-nerd.com/SRC/
Author: Erik de Castro Lopo
License: GPL V2

Directory: deps/sndfile
The sndfile library can be found at:
http://www.mega-nerd.com/libsndfile/
Author: Erik de Castro Lopo
License: GPL V2.1
The sndfile wrapper is adapted from:
https://github.com/p0nce/DerelictSndFile
Author: ponce
License: Public Domain
